I envy those who had the willpower to leave EQ. I've 'quit' 3 or 4 times now, always to come back. Spent money on other games, just to have it wasted coming back to EQ.<br>
<br>
DAoC, for example. I bought that, I have a few RL friends that left EQ a long time ago and started playing. My plan was to play DAoC full-time to try and let EQ's pull diminish. <br>
Guess what didn't work.<br>
While I enjoy DAoC, there is just something about EQ....something more and more people are picking up every day.<br>
<br>
